<section id="blog" class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 text-base font-medium text-indigo-600 bg-indigo-50 rounded-full mb-4">
        博客文章
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">AI智能体领域的最新洞察</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600">
        探索前沿AI技术趋势，了解智能体如何改变各行各业的工作方式。
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Blog Card 1 -->
      <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300">
        <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-500 to-purple-600 relative">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-wave-pattern opacity-10"></div>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
            <i data-lucide="trending-up" class="w-12 h-12 text-white opacity-80"></i>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 mb-4">
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 text-xs rounded-full">趋势</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">2024-06-20</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">2024年AI智能体发展趋势报告</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">
            深入分析今年AI智能体领域的关键趋势、技术突破和行业变革，预测未来发展方向。
          </p>
          <a href="#" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-700 text-sm font-medium flex items-center">
            阅读全文
            <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-4 h-4 ml-1"></i>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Blog Card 2 -->
      <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300">
        <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-cyan-600 relative">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-wave-pattern opacity-10"></div>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
            <i data-lucide="lightbulb" class="w-12 h-12 text-white opacity-80"></i>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 mb-4">
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-green-50 text-green-600 text-xs rounded-full">实践</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">2024-06-15</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">如何打造一个高效的企业级智能体</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">
            从需求分析到实施部署，一步步指导企业构建符合业务需求的专属智能体系统。
          </p>
          <a href="#" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-700 text-sm font-medium flex items-center">
            阅读全文
            <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-4 h-4 ml-1"></i>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Blog Card 3 -->
      <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300">
        <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-500 to-orange-600 relative">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-wave-pattern opacity-10"></div>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
            <i data-lucide="briefcase" class="w-12 h-12 text-white opacity-80"></i>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 mb-4">
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-orange-50 text-orange-600 text-xs rounded-full">案例</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">2024-06-08</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">扣子智能体如何帮助金融企业提升效率</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">
            深度解析某大型金融机构如何通过扣子智能体优化客户服务流程，降低成本同时提升满意度。
          </p>
          <a href="#" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-700 text-sm font-medium flex items-center">
            阅读全文
            <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-4 h-4 ml-1"></i>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="mt-12 text-center">
      <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
        查看更多文章
        <i data-lucide="chevron-right" class="w-4 h-4 ml-2"></i>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>